snippet.title: Eat Your Words - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Eat Your Words is a fun game for people that love word games. It is a unique mashup of a traditional word puzzle game and a candy/gem collecting game.

The goal of the game is to find as many words as you can on the game board. Each word must be at least 3 letters, and you can't use the same word twice. Every word generates sushi pieces. Match 3 sushi pieces to clear them off the board.

Eat Your Words (C) Johnny Ow
